original purethermal library from: https://github.com/Kheirlb/purethermal1-uvc-capture
compiled using the following commands:


This was selected over the default library for ease of build and use (especially ratiometric mode) on rasberry pi

the following command was used to update rasberry pi (the easy way):
curl https://get.pimoroni.com/uptodate | bash

the hard way would have been:
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get upgrade
sudo reboot